    "Note that the identification of samples with short-cuts are completed at the same time by asking GPT-4 to first check before modifying the answers (details in Appendix.2).",
    "We removed samples whose candidate answers are the same as the original ones as these samples are identified by the GPT-4 as qualified samples without VA and QA short-cuts.",
